    <item>
      <title>台湾官员称中国军队最近实行克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-military-exercising-restraint-lately-taiwan-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾安全官员表示，中国似乎正在减弱对台湾的军事压力，并警告北京仍可能继续其外交孤立行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-military-exercising-restraint-lately-taiwan-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯警告全球选举临近之际虚假信息“泛滥”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/blinken-warns-of-false-info-flood-as-elections-loom-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯警告称，威权政府将干预一系列选举，美国将继续施压，阻止中国和俄罗斯散布虚假信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/blinken-warns-of-false-info-flood-as-elections-loom-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:04:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
